sentences: Ferus Mustafov, also known as King Ferus Mustafov (born December 20, 1950) ,is a Macedonian saxophonist of Romani descent.

Following a year of military service, during which he established his reputation playing at evening dances, he moved to Sarajevo, Bosnia and Herzegovina, where he took a leading role in the explosion in popularity of folk music taking place there at the time.
